item.title: CVE-2018-5387|2024-08-05T05:33:44.367Z -- wizkunde -- samlbase
item.description: Wizkunde SAMLBase may incorrectly utilize the results of XML DOM traversal and canonicalization APIs in such a way that an attacker may be able to manipulate the SAML data without invalidating the cryptographic signature, allowing the attack to potentially bypass authentication to SAML service providers.
